description:
Originally labelled FT2-692, this ticket will now represent the work to do location/activity changes.
    As a participant, I need to update the activity of the dog so that I fulfull GRV compliance requirements.
    As a Participant receiving a dog from another Participant, I need to select the address at which the dog is physically located so that the location of the dog is known
name: FT2-10076-Dog Location-Change Dog Activity/Location

elements.name: QA-443: Verify the Breeder can able to Remove the dog from kennel

steps.name: A participant "William Mcmahon" logged in to FastTrack application
user navigates to 'I Want To' -> 'Kennel' tab and clicks 'Remove from Kennel' tab
user selects the dog and clicks agree to remove dog from kennel
user should be able to verify the dog details
